{"tid":1685363,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《港詭實錄》恐怖冒險遊戲 融合香港都市傳說與真實案件","createTime":"2019-10-31T13:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T14:07:41.000Z","uid":321748,"like":6,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2f460e71b85bf4e28bbddac8fa3f2587fc6050ea","tid":1685363,"uid":321748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:25:03.000Z","msg":"《港詭實錄》&shy;是一款以現代香港為背景的恐怖冒險遊戲，融合了香港本地的都市傳說與真實案件。<br />\n玩家能夠從中體驗到許多獨特的香港本地文化和民俗習慣。同時，在遊戲中我們還原了唐樓、粵劇戲棚、公共屋邨等極具香港特色的建築，讓各位自由探索的同時，感受濃厚的香港氣息。<br />\n通過這款遊戲，我們想讓更多人可以去了解民俗，了解傳統文化，了解香港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lUGpivp94IQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlUGpivp94IQ&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eGINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=11dd62d8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lUGpivp94IQ</a>"},{"pid":"0601ec6e224e208c633442c49d4a0cc01cc093c6","tid":1685363,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:34:11.000Z","msg":"還願"},{"pid":"6fbb910c356824371684b666a76e584afd9d6962","tid":1685363,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:35:39.000Z","msg":"太似還願"},{"pid":"61b8ca1cb41b68038356a53306f72e073bac68d1","tid":1685363,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:37:26.000Z","msg":"期待"},{"pid":"92ca7277a92c9a8f517400304aeb68dd9ab14107","tid":1685363,"uid":67574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0601ec6e224e208c633442c49d4a0cc01cc093c6","tid":1685363,"uid":8290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:34:11.000Z","msg":"還願"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T13:38:53.000Z","msg":"港版還願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f2b62e8aa593b03c0cf44c2e85dd5f074be3131","tid":1685363,"uid":136624,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T17:37:33.000Z","msg":"咪撚買 奶共既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c997c837895bb8